title: Headhunterz - Hard With Style - Episode #1
description:
Headhunterz presents: Hard With Style - Episode #1

After years of playing at clubs and events all over the world, worlds #1 Hardstyle DJ thought it was time to add a little extra flavour. Headhunterz presents \'Hard With Style\' a new monthly podcast for 2011.

Compiled to keep you updated about the freshest banging beats from around the globe, \'Hard with Style\' will give you a very personal approach to presenting Headhunterz\' favorite tracks of the moment via iTunes and direct download.

iTunes:
Direct download:

Headhunterz is known world-wide for his passion and energy for hard music both on an off the stage, representing his unique style at every major event including Defqon.1, Hard Bass, Qlimax, In Qontrol and Decibel. \'Hard With Style\' is no exception, with each show containing the upmost quality and the freshest tunes.
